It has been 3 1/2 years since I last wrote here.&nbsp; I mainly stopped writing cause I moved home and the people I was was trying to keep up with were now close enough to talk to in person.
Those years has seen some changes.&nbsp; I now have 2 nephews and a niece.&nbsp; And we all live in the same province.&nbsp; A good friend passed away from breast cancer.&nbsp; I had a term contract and have been thinking about going for my masters.&nbsp; I have 2 more tattoos.&nbsp; I have developed a new intrest and am involved in a social group.&nbsp; 
Somethings haven't changed.&nbsp; Still prefer girls.&nbsp; Still love fanfiction.&nbsp; Same #$%^&amp; computer.&nbsp; Still can't seem to finish any of my writing projects, unless it is poetry.
